                <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
                <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
                <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
                <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
            </continued></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412787097_011" name="2" temporalId="s14_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>凡不能按照第(1)款向某人送達的文件在總監不時藉憲報公告指明的公眾地方展示為期不少於4天，該文件須當作已妥為送達該人。</content></subsection></section></part></main></subLeg>